{flag|Mongolia}}\n|Nat\u00e1lia Pereira<br/>{{flag|Portugal}}\n| colspan=\"4\" rowspan=\"4\" {{n/a|Not awarded}}\n|-\n|2015\n|Dalma Karman<br/>{{flag|Hungary}}\n|Marina Stelmakh<br/>{{flag|Ukraine}}\n|Alexandra Efstathiadi<br/>{{flag|Greece}}\n|Stefany Merlin<br/>{{flag|Venezuela}}\n|-\n|2014\n|Nisheeka Lal<br/>{{flag|Fiji}}\n|Stefanie-Jayne Williams<br/>{{flag|England}}\n|Maddison Clare Sloane<br/>{{flag|Australia}}\n|Chen Xiao-Wen<br/>{{flag|Taiwan}}\n|-\n|2013\n|Li Mi<br/>{{flag|Bangladesh}}\n|Shasha Chen<br/>{{flag|China}}\n|Fonthip Klinpakdee<br/>{{flag|Thailand}}\n|Yana Haenisch<br/>{{flag|Namibia}}\n|-\n|2012\n| colspan=\"4\" {{n/a|Not awarded}}\n|Novell Tan Yu Xuan<br/>{{flag|Singapore}}\n|Cynthia Lowen<br/>{{flag|Canada}}\n|Pimchan Phichayasut<br/>{{flag|Thailand}}\n|Anastasiya Gavrilova<br/>{{flag|Russia}}\n|}\n\n==See also==\n* [[List of beauty contests]]\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n*[https://www.faceofbeautyinternational.com/ Official website]\n*{{Facebook|FaceBeautyInternational}} Page\n\n[[Category:Miss International| ]]\n[[Category:International beauty pageants]]\n[[Category:Recurring events established in 2012]]\n", "text_old": "{{Infobox organization\n| name = Face of Beauty International\n| image = \n| image_border = \n| size = \n| caption = \n| map = \n| msize = \n| mcaption = \n| motto = \n| formation = 2012\n| type = [[Beauty pageant]]\n| headquarters = [[Auckland]], [[New Zealand]]\n| location = [[Auckland]], [[New Zealand]]\n| membership = \n| language = [[English language|English]]\n| leader_title = President\n| leader_name = Mila Manuel\n| key_people = \n| num_staff = \n| budget = \n| website = [https://www.faceofbeautyinternational.com FACE OF BEAUTY INTERNATIONAL]\n}}\n\n'''Face of Beauty International''' is an annual female beauty pageant founded in 2012. \n\nThe incumbent Miss Face of Beauty International is [[Peerachada Khunrak]] of [[Thailand]] who was crowned on 17 November 2019 in Manila, Philippines.<ref name=\"thepageantcrown_2019-09\">{{cite web|url=https://thepageantcrown.blogspot.com/2018/09/face-of-beauty-international-2018.html|title=May wins Face of Beauty International 2018|last=|first=|date=9 September 2018|website=|publisher=|url-status=live|archive-url=|archive-date=|access-date=}}</ref>\nThe Teen Face of Beauty International is Leia Edmonds from New Zealand. Also crowned 17 November 2019.\n\n== Host countries and venues ==\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\" border=\"2\" cellpadding=\"2\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin: 0 1em 0 0; background: #f9f9f9; border: 1px #aaa solid; border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 95%;\"\n|- bgcolor=\"efefef\"\n!Edition\n!Year\n!Date\n!Venue\n!Host country\n!Number of Entrants\n|-\n|1st\n|2012\n|December 18\n|Valentine Garden Resort, [[Chiang Mai Province|Chiang Mai]]\n|{{flag|Thailand}}\n|14\n|-\n|2nd\n|2013\n|November 12\n|Mimosa Pattaya, [[Sattahip District|Na Chom Thian]], [[Chonburi Province|Chonburi]]\n|{{flag|Thailand}}\n|37\n|-\n|3rd\n|2014\n|November 15\n|New Palace Grand Ballroom, [[Taichung]]\n|{{flag|Taiwan}}\n|38\n|-\n|4th\n|2015\n|October 15\n|[[Kaohsiung Grand Hotel|The Grand Hotel]], [[Kaohsiung]]\n|{{flag|Taiwan}}\n|42\n|-\n|5th\n|2016\n|October 8\n|The Corporate Hotel & Convention Centre, [[Ulaanbaatar]]\n|{{flag|Mongolia}}\n|47\n|-\n|6th\n|2017\n|September 23\n|The Vintage Royal Pandals at CBD Ground, [[New Delhi]]\n|{{flag|India}}\n|40\n|-\n|7th\n|2018\n|September 17\n|City Park Resort, [[New Delhi]]\n|{{flag|India}}\n|42\n|-\n|8th\n|2019\n|November 17\n|Royce Hotel and Casino, [[Pampanga]]\n|{{flag|Philippines}}\n|37\n|-\n|9th\n|2020\n|''TBA''\n|''TBA''\n|''TBA''\n|''TBA''\n|}\n\n== Recent titleholders ==\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\" font-size: 95%;\"\n! rowspan=\"2\" |Edition\n! colspan=\"2\" |Face Of Beauty International\n! colspan=\"2\" |Teen Face Of Beauty International\n|- align=\"centre\" colspan=\"10\"\n! width=\"180\" |Country\n! width=\"180\" |Winner\n! width=\"180\" |Country\n! width=\"180\" |