pan=\"2\" {{n/a|Not awarded}} \n|{{flag|Denmark}}\n| Josefine Egebjerg <ref>{{cite web|title=Josefine Emilie Egebjerg \u2013 Miss Teen Face of Beauty International 2012!||url=http://missosology.org/other-pageants/face-of-beauty-international/22247-face-of-beauty-international-2015-kaohsiung-taiwan-is-the-host-country/attachment/josefine-emilie-egebjerg-miss-teen-face-of-beauty-international-2012-1/}}</ref>\n|-\n|}\n\n=== Countries by number of title wins ===\n\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\" border=\"5\" cellpadding=\"3\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin: 1em 1em 1em 0; background: #FFFFFF; border: 1px #aaa solid; border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 95%;\"\n! colspan=\"3\" |Face Of Beauty International\n! colspan=\"3\" |Teen Face Of Beauty International\n|- bgcolor=\"#787878\" colspan=\"10\" ali\n! Country/Territory\n! Titles\n! Year\n!Country/Territory\n!Titles\n!Year\n|-\n|{{flag|Thailand}}\n|style=\"text-align:center;\" |2\n|2017, 2019\n|{{flag|New Zealand}}\n| rowspan=\"6\" style=\"text-align:center;\" |1\n|2019\n|-\n|{{flag|Myanmar}}\n| rowspan=\"6\" style=\"text-align:center;\" | 1\n|2018\n|{{flag|Benelux}}\n|2018\n|-\n|{{flag|Russia}}\n|2016\n|{{flag|South Africa}}\n|2017\n|-\n|{{flag|Mexico}}\n|2015\n|{{flag|Myanmar}}\n|2016\n|-\n|{{flag|Argentina}}\n|2014\n|{{flag|Puerto Rico}}\n|2015\n|-\n|{{flag|Tonga}}\n|2013\n|{{flag|Denmark}}\n|2012\n|-\n|}\n\n== List of runners-up ==\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\" border=\"5\" cellpadding=\"3\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin: 1em 1em 1em 0; background: #FFFFFF; border: 1px #aaa solid; border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 80%; text-align:center;\" |\n|-style=\" background:#787878;\" \n! rowspan=\"2\" |Year\n! colspan=\"4\" |Face Of Beauty International\n! colspan=\"4\" |Teen Face Of Beauty International\n|-\n! width=\"200\" |1st Runner-Up\n! width=\"200\" |2nd Runner-Up\n! width=\"200\" |3rd Runner-Up\n! width=\"250\" |4th Runner-Up\n! width=\"200\" |1st Runner-Up\n! width=\"200\" |2nd Runner-Up\n! width=\"200\